code: @Override public WebServiceConnection createConnection(URI uri) throws IOException {     try {         return new CamelDirectConnection(camelContext, uri).     } catch (URISyntaxException e) {         throw new IOException(e).     } }
@Override public boolean supports(URI uri) {     try {         new CamelDirectConnection(camelContext, uri).         return true.     } catch (URISyntaxException e) {         return false.     } }
public void setCamelContext(CamelContext camelContext) {     this.camelContext = camelContext. }
